一切回歸三個字 &ndash; 真普選</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">核心訴求只有一個：真普選，一切口號、行動、宣傳，都環繞真普選這單一訴求展開，<strong>這樣，世界聽得懂，連中國內地人民都聽得懂</strong>。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"80f55172858e3fea0444e0ea97fa7f0313a6e614","tid":1728744,"uid":60049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:09:20.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"81dd755bdca3febe819da1fbf5ce368b88bf651a","tid":1728744,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:09:29.000Z","msg":"搞笑post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09567373f984b4695c4d53adce097a71a9d3d24d","tid":1728744,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:09:40.000Z","msg":"****眾籌****<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>分化post 不幫你推POST<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n鍾庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先64%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第五期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1</a> <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUzzBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=be96cf92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUzzBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=f0821a07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"30888e438f53584d2a7aa0efef779df69447a7ad","tid":1728744,"uid":35894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:10:13.000Z","msg":"又一城同中大佢都係到<br />\n你又係邊撚到？"},{"pid":"06e7ef9b85c9a9b4692208ea7b30b505745f8875","tid":1728744,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30888e438f53584d2a7aa0efef779df69447a7ad","tid":1728744,"uid":35894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:10:13.000Z","msg":"又一城同中大佢都係到<br />\n你又係邊撚到？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:10:37.000Z","msg":"分化撚 日日都要搵人嚟分化<br />\n唔駛太認真"},{"pid":"df0ff02c5509fb43ff6a7a4825b1eb3e36880915","tid":1728744,"uid":34787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:11:21.000Z","msg":"不推文回覆"},{"pid":"25060757dd1a68f826f6cf213d73d215721b5304","tid":1728744,"uid":294100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c6d261f401a54d1ef55c53426e74aa2a04e334f","tid":1728744,"uid":254813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:02:19.000Z","msg":"好似無？對的，飯碗最緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:11:23.000Z","msg":"番屋企打飛機啦屌你"},{"pid":"d9192708500e781cb4398d63481bdfa9f49f4d45","tid":1728744,"uid":338084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:11:43.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"773f6029bc1a4c9